er><h4 class=tj-project-7-title>FOOD</h4><div class=tj-project-7-paragraph><p>Captured & Shared by <code>@ch3ryyl</code></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=tj-service-9-area id=recruitment><div class=container><div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="section-header text-center style-5"><div class=sec-text><span class=subtitle data-wow-delay=.3s>Open Positions</span><h2 class="title tj-text-invert">Be part of the journey with FAMZ</h2></div></div></div><div class=row><div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xl-4"><div class="wow fadeInUp tj-service-6-wrapper"data-wow-delay=.3s><div class=tj-service-6-icon><span><img alt=""src=assets/img/icons/service-6-icon1.svg></span></div><div class=tj-service-6-content><h4 class=tj-service-6-title>Programee Director</h4><div class=tj-service-6-paragraph><p>Leads planning and hosting creative events, podcasts, and live sessions to keep FAMZ active and engaging. Sparks collaboration and shared moments among members through fresh ideas.<ul><li>Event Planning<li>Content Creation<li>Community Engagement</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xl-4"><div class="wow fadeInUp tj-service-6-wrapper"data-wow-delay=.5s><div class=tj-service-6-icon><span><img alt=""src=assets/img/icons/service-6-icon2.svg></span></div><div class=tj-service-6-content><h4 class=tj-service-6-title><a href=#service-wrapper class=modal-popup>Community Staff & Management</a></h4><div class=tj-service-6-paragraph><p>Moderates discussions and daily operations to keep FAMZ welcoming and organized. Supports members, maintains harmony, and ensures every voice feels valued in the community.<ul><li>Moderation<li>Member Support</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xl-4"><div class="wow fadeInUp tj-service-6-wrapper"data-wow-delay=.7s><div class=tj-service-6-icon><span><img alt=""src=assets/img/icons/service-6-icon3.svg></span></div><div class=tj-service-6-content><h4 class=tj-serv