dn.discordapp.com/avatars/508450520663326730/1d60294fad7a8503a6110638202b0a10.png?format=webp&quality=lossless&width=920&height=920"></div><div class=feature-content><h4 class=name>justiqar</h4><span class=designation>FAMZ /fæmz/</span></div></div></div></div><div class=swiper-slide><div class="wow fadeInUp style-8 testimonial-item"data-wow-delay=.5s><div class=icon-box><svg viewBox="0 0 22 22"height=22 width=22 fill=none xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg><path d="M0.105431 2.18998C0.0301532 0.988687 1.02531 -0.00647222 2.2266 0.0688056L19.4961 1.15097C21.2148 1.25867 22.0029 3.34358 20.7852 4.56127L4.5979 20.7486C3.3802 21.9663 1.2953 21.1781 1.1876 19.4594L0.105431 2.18998Z"fill=url(#paint2_linear_263_588) /><defs><linearGradient gradientUnits=userSpaceOnUse id=paint2_linear_263_588 x1=-0.0363755 x2=35.3333 y1=-0.0729998 y2=-0.0729991><stop offset=1 stop-color=var(--tj-theme-primary) /><stop offset=1 stop-color=#140C1C stop-opacity=0 /></linearGradient></defs></svg> <svg viewBox="0 0 22 22"height=22 width=22 fill=none xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg><path d="M0.105431 2.18998C0.0301532 0.988687 1.02531 -0.00647222 2.2266 0.0688056L19.4961 1.15097C21.2148 1.25867 22.0029 3.34358 20.7852 4.56127L4.5979 20.7486C3.3802 21.9663 1.2953 21.1781 1.1876 19.4594L0.105431 2.18998Z"fill=url(#paint2_linear_263_589) /><defs><linearGradient gradientUnits=userSpaceOnUse id=paint2_linear_263_589 x1=-0.0363755 x2=35.3333 y1=-0.0729998 y2=-0.0729991><stop offset=1 stop-color=var(--tj-theme-primary) /><stop offset=1 stop-color=#140C1C stop-opacity=0 /></linearGradient></defs></svg></div><p class=quote>Helps FAMZ grow by building meaningful partnerships and collaborations that bring fresh stories, events, and opportunities.<div class=testimonial-feature-item><div class=auother-images><img alt=Images src="https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/0vJwLLKnV4vgrJH-pegBrZkCG6pxe9kK7EGZNf490Hk/%3Fsize%3D1024/https/cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1311656983698472960/05bb43d329919b53d216a69e0b0a947d.png?format=webp&quality=lossless&width=320&height=320"></div><div class=feature-content><h4 class=name>zero.t7</h4><span class=designation>FAMZ /fæmz/</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class=testimonial-pagination></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=faq-section id=faq><div class=container><div class=row><div class=col-md-12><div class="section-header text-center"><h2 class="wow fadeInUp section-title"data-wow-delay=.3s>Frequently Asked Questions</h2></div></div></div><div class=row><div class=col-12><div class="accordion tj-faq"id=faqOne><div class="wow fadeInUp accordion-item active"data-wow-delay=.4s><button aria-expanded=true class=faq-title data-bs-target=#faq-1 data-bs-toggle=collapse type=button>What is FAMZ?</button><div class="collapse show"id=faq-1 data-bs-parent=#faqOne><div class="accordion-body faq-text"><p>FAMZ is a modern Discord community built for creative minds, discussions, and collaboration. We host events, podcasts, contests, and more to keep the community active and engaging.</div></div></div><div class="wow fadeInUp accordion-item"data-wow-delay=.5s><button aria-expanded=false class="faq-title collapsed"data-bs-target=#faq-2 data-bs-toggle=collapse type=button>How can I support FAMZ?</button><div class=collapse id=faq-2 data-bs-parent=#faqOne><div class="accordion-body faq-text"><p>You can support us by donating via Saweria. We offer Supporter and Super Supporter roles, plus perks like custom roles for bigger contributions. Your support helps keep FAMZ growing.</div></div></div><div class="wow fadeInUp accordion-item"data-wow-delay=.6s><button aria-expanded=false class="faq-title collapsed"data-bs-target=#faq-3 data-bs-toggle=collapse type=button>What is Partner Ping?</button><div class=collapse id=faq-3 data-bs-parent=#faqOne><div class="accordion-body faq-text"><p>Partner Ping is an optional role that lets you get notified about partner announcements and events from our network. You can claim or remove it anytime via <code>#self-role.</code></div></div></div><div class="wow fadeInUp accordion-item"data-wow-delay=.7s><button aria-expanded=false class="faq-title collapsed"data-bs-target=#faq-4 data-bs-toggle=collapse type=button>What is the server’s main language?</button><div class=collapse id=faq-4 data-bs-parent=#faqOne><div class="accordion-body faq-text"><p>FAMZ is bilingual. We mainly use Indonesian and English to keep it inclusive and open to everyone.</div></div></div><div class="wow fadeInUp accordion-item"data-wow-delay=.8s><button aria-expanded=false class="faq-title collapsed"data-bs-target=#faq-5 data-bs-toggle=collapse type=button>How can I get roles?</button><div class=collapse id=faq-5 data-bs-parent=#faqOne><div class="accordion-body faq-text"><p>You can claim roles by using our self-role feature in the <code>#self-roles</code> channel. We offer game roles and event roles like Partner Ping.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=text-section><div class=container><div class=row><div class=col-12><div class=section-header><div class=heading-left><p class="wow fadeInUp"data-wow-delay=.3s>Join the journey<h2 class="wow fadeInUp section-title"data-wow-delay=.4s id=anim>FAMZ on Discord</h2></div><div class="wow fadeInRight chat-mail"data-wow-delay=.5s><a href=https://discord.gg/famz target=_blank class=link>discord.gg/famz<i class="fa-arrow-right fa-light"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div></section></main><section class="style-8 tj-footer-7-area"><div class=container><div class=row><div class=col-12><div class=tj-footer-7-bottom><div class=container><div class=row><div class=col><div class=tj-footer-7-wrapper><div class=tj-footer-6-left><p class=tj-footer-6-paragraph>BOT STATUS ONLINE</div><div class=tj-footer-7-middle><div class="header-media tj-header-5-right-media"><ul class="social-icons tj-header-5-right-social-icons ul-reset"><li><a href=https://discord.gg/famz target=_blank><i class="fa-brands fa-discord"></i></a><li><a hre